T1  - Exposure to collective gender-based violence causes intimate partner violence
AU  - Stojetz, Wolfgang
AU  - Brück, Tilman
JO  - Journal of Development Economics
VL  - 164
SP  - 103054
PY  - 2023
DA  - 2023/09/01/
